{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act42side", "eventName": "眾生行記", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "MT-3", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "禮拜", "storyInfo": "調查爆炸案的蕾繆安跟著線索追查到了育嬰聖堂，但牧首拒絕讓她參與育嬰聖堂的安防工作。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "61_g2_baptismlobby", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$tech_intro", "key": "$tech_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1780_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薇爾麗芙樞機，好久不見。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1780_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別叫樞機了，我現在只是育嬰聖堂裡一個再普通不過的事務員。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#1$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我叫你前輩囉……看起來，確實是前輩的手筆。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1780_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼？", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#4$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我剛剛一路走來看見的，從外圍街道到聖堂內部，這裡的安防設計完全不輸戍衛隊。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1780_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總得幫忙做一點工作嘛。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#11$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1780_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "話說回來，還真的被我猜對了。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#1$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#6$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼？", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#6$2"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1780_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來這裡確認防務的果然是你……從程序上來說，這種工作明顯更適合公證所的執行者，或是銃騎與戍衛隊的成員。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#1$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我目前也還在追查前兩天的爆炸事件哦，不是什麼無關人士。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1780_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還沒接到通知說布防的時候要把爆炸案的調查結果也考慮在內，況且，你的調查現在也還沒有什麼實際的成果吧？", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#2$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1780_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道說，你來這裡，是因為受到襲擊的是安多恩？", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#1$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#8$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#8$2"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#2$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前輩，你不會是想警告我，身為七廳樞機，眼裡應該是整座聖城，而不是自己的私交吧？", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#2$2"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1780_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，我們都知道你是什麼樣的人啦。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#3$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1780_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "頭腦清醒，做事雷厲風行，又有敏銳準確的洞察力，在遴選樞機的時候確實加了很多分……", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#1$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但大家也都清楚，你的這些美好品格，一般在什麼時候最能體現出來。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#1$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1780_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蕾繆安樞機，我還記得你當年加入戍衛隊特勤隊的初衷哦，我看過那份報告書。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#8$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，是嗎，我都忘了。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1780_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你本來並沒有打算加入特勤隊，只是去看望菲亞梅塔的，對吧？", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#1$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#2$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……還有安多恩。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#2$2"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1780_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦？這我倒是不知道。我以為你們是加入特勤隊之後才認識的。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#1$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#2$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更早之前。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#2$2"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#8$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他好像是從很遠的地方一路走過來的，穿著一身破衣裳，十分憔悴。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#8$2"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就那麼一動不動地坐在禮拜堂前的長椅上，比路邊的聖徒像更像聖徒像。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#8$2"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#2$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是我和莫斯提馬第一次見到他。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#2$2"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於菲亞梅塔，本來就是我和莫斯提馬在電影院午夜場偶然認識的好朋友。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安多恩不在聖城長大，本身就格格不入；菲亞梅塔的個性固執不服輸，當時大概在和她的爺爺賭氣……我和莫斯提馬就想說去看看。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這兩人事先並不認識，其他的薩科塔也未必是故意排擠他們，但實際的結果是——", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#2$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "整個“軟膠銃彈輪盤，暨特勤隊組隊儀式”，就只有這兩個傢伙孤零零地被剩了下來。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#2$2"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1780_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以你就把在場的其他人都痛扁了一頓……", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#2$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "又和莫斯提馬當場填了申請表，跟他們組成了那次組隊儀式的最後一個四人小隊。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#2$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後成了整個特勤隊出外勤次數最多、配合最有默契的小隊，也才有了後來的意外……", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#2$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1780_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蕾繆安，不論我再怎麼欣賞你……我也還是要提醒你，身處樞機之位，做事的出發點就永遠只有聖城。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#9$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖城在我眼裡，首先是一個又一個熟悉的名字。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#2$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前輩，懷舊到此為止。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#2$2"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#8$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "第七廳有能力審視自己的職責所在。如果前輩只以“普通的事務員”自居，我應該親自去見一下牧首。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#8$2"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1780_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#9$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#8$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她就在前面，對吧？", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#8$2"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_churchfootstep", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "61_i06", "block": "false", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.15, "yScaleFrom": 1.15, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 70.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蕾繆安見到了此行的目標。"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "金髮薩科塔立於某道門廊之下，她在禱告，她在不安，她的呼吸急促，身體因此肉眼可見地顫慄著……"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蕾繆安感覺自己快被對方洶湧的情緒淹沒了。"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "牧首？", "name": "蕾繆安"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——", "name": "牧首"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蕾繆安樞機，我聽到了你和薇爾麗芙的談話……但請原諒我此刻無法思緒平靜地與你交談。", "name": "牧首"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在那裡面的是？", "name": "蕾繆安"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一位薩卡茲母親。", "name": "牧首"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她在荒野上耽擱了太久，來這裡又拒食了兩天……現在的情況不容樂觀。我們的保育員正在為她治療。", "name": "牧首"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她在恐懼，她在焦躁，她不想輸給疼痛，此刻仍在掙扎著保持清醒……", "name": "牧首"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……她在清醒地祈禱，祈禱孩子能平安降生。", "name": "牧首"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能做的，只是與她感同身受，與她一同祈禱。", "name": "牧首"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您能感受到薩卡茲的情緒？", "name": "蕾繆安"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，樞機。", "name": "牧首"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像此刻，你也在為我的悸動而擔憂。它清晰得如同你我之間與生俱來的共感。", "name": "牧首"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“共感”……", "name": "蕾繆安"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許這是主對我這樣一個目盲者額外的恩典，也許只是因為……這裡是拉特蘭專為創造新生而建的聖堂。", "name": "牧首"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的信仰將在此打下基礎，在此延伸，這裡不應該有任何隔閡與限制。", "name": "牧首"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣說來，更應該走進這裡的，是我們的同胞自己。", "name": "牧首"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "蕾繆安"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陽光從高處的彩窗落下，照亮空曠而肅穆的大廳。"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "巨大的聖像俯首合十，注視著下方兩位渺小的薩科塔。"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡的確很特別。", "name": "蕾繆安"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "見識過許多用各種奇怪姿勢舉著銃蓄勢待發的聖像，第一次見到這種造型的，還真是，嗯，有點不太習慣……", "name": "蕾繆安"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "相比於矗立在玻利瓦爾山間或伊比利亞海邊的那些所謂的“拉特蘭教造像”，拉特蘭隨處可見的聖像其實更難以理解，樞機。", "name": "牧首"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "樂園形塑了我們別樣到有些失真的虔誠。", "name": "牧首"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "跋涉在天災與苦難中的生靈，為生存祈願……這才是信仰最初的形貌。", "name": "牧首"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "hidecgitem", "attributes": {"image": "cgitem_61_i06"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "61_g2_baptismlobby", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1785_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "牧、牧首，一切平安。", "name": "保育員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1785_1#1$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那位母親的狀態終於平復下來了，我們餵她吃了藥，也幫她補充了營養，此刻她已經睡著了。", "name": "保育員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1785_1#1$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼——那我就放心了。", "name": "牧首"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她分娩在即，還請繼續注意她的狀況，不得有一絲鬆懈。", "name": "牧首"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1785_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是。", "name": "保育員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1785_1#1$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感恩主的賜福。", "name": "牧首"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能感受到，您發自內心的釋然與喜悅。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也感謝你的陪伴，樞機。希望共感沒有讓我的不安影響到你。", "name": "牧首"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#9$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不會，我沒有那麼脆弱啦。再說，您剛剛的話對我也有一些啟發。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#9$2"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽您剛剛說起……您好像是後面才來到這裡的？", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。", "name": "牧首"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我曾在荒野間踟躕良久，我的同行者們凋敝於泥污……", "name": "牧首"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了找到拉特蘭？", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#14$2"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，彼時我從未想過，大地上會出現這樣一座城市。", "name": "牧首"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但共同的願景，讓我終於找到了它的位置。", "name": "牧首"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們能在此時此刻相遇，這是被寫就的命運，樞機。", "name": "牧首"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所幸過了這麼久，以我之殘軀，仍然能為拉特蘭、為我的族人們做一點事情。", "name": "牧首"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的一位朋友，他也在這座聖堂中工作，他也是從遙遠的地方來到這裡……", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如今的拉特蘭，未來的拉特蘭，每一個人都必須，也能夠找到自己的位置，發揮各自的作用……由此，我們才能對抗災異。", "name": "牧首"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "話題扯太遠了。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然出現了針對保育員的襲擊事件，第七廳願意協助育嬰聖堂加強安防工作，確保降生儀式能夠順利進行。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "牧首"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "樞機，我理解你對朋友的擔憂，也理解你對這座聖堂的好奇……", "name": "牧首"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但如我方才所說，我們每個人都應該在各自的位置，發揮各自的作用。", "name": "牧首"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1777_1#1$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#2$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，我本來還以為我們聊得蠻開心的。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#2$2"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但結果是……我被無情地拒絕了，對吧？", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "39_g1_monasteryentrance", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$calm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1784_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……節哀順變啊，各位。", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#3$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "早知道這裡發生了這樣的事情，出門時我應該帶幾株麥穗的。", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#3$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "麥穗？", "name": "庫蘭塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1784_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蘭登修道院的葬禮會有些特別的儀式。我們會用麥穗編一頂髮冠，放在死者的棺槨上。", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#3$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣，他在彼岸也能聞到麵包和啤酒的香味，靈魂就會得到撫慰。", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#3$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝你，好心的修女。", "name": "庫蘭塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我和我的兄弟因為感染了礦石病，又沒有參加騎士競技的能力，只能被商業聯合會驅逐，就這麼流浪荒野。", "name": "庫蘭塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好不容易來到了拉特蘭，他卻在這時候發病去世了……想想也真的很倒楣。", "name": "庫蘭塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，教皇廳幫我安葬了他。他死得還算體面……甚至還有一位路過的薩科塔為他演奏了哀歌。", "name": "庫蘭塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1784_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣啊……", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#6$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請確認，你所見的薩科塔，是否為黑色長直髮，女性，所持的樂器是一架形制特殊的大提琴？", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，是。", "name": "庫蘭塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她對你們進行了演奏？", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在她的演奏過程中，你們是否感受到了幻覺，或者某種精神層面的不適？", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不適是指？反正聽得我蠻想哭的，畢竟那是我的兄弟啊……", "name": "庫蘭塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1784_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "執行者先生，不是說好了，我來負責打探……", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#6$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "公證所的其他執行者很快就會接這群流浪者到安布羅修區的安置點，我們的時間本就不多。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "流浪者也並非嫌犯，我不覺得有必要對他們使用迂迴的詢問策略。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1784_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以前為了幫蘭登修道院做宣傳，我去過龍門，也去過維多利亞……我經常見到這樣的人。", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#3$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為種種不幸的遭遇，他們才離開自己的國家。他們大多和警察打過交道，對警察的態度都很……", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#3$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "執行者相當於警察，對吧？", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#3$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，沒有必要啦，畢竟你們剛收留了我們這些異族的感染者。好像以前你們自己的公民感染了礦石病，都是要被趕走的。", "name": "庫蘭塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以我現在對拉特蘭官方的印象還不錯，再說這位先生感覺也很正直……", "name": "庫蘭塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1784_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#3$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於你們剛剛想問的那位黑髮薩科塔，她有什麼問題嗎？", "name": "庫蘭塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "該薩科塔目前處於受監管狀態。她擅自從修道院離開，我們一路調查她的行蹤來到這裡。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她、她是囚犯？我還以為她是你們第六廳的公務員呢。", "name": "庫蘭塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你依據什麼作出這樣的判斷？", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_001", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "葬禮結束後，她向我們確認了修道院的情況——有沒有哪些設施年久失修、潛在危險或急缺的物資之類的。", "name": "庫蘭塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦對了，她還專門問過，最近剛到拉特蘭的人裡有沒有誰突然不見了，尤其是孕婦……", "name": "庫蘭塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_001"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1784_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（聽起來，阿爾圖羅小姐不像是偶然經過啊……）", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#3$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "61_g3_nurserytemplecorridor", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1780_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼樣？", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#1$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#2$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "何必問呢，前輩。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#2$2"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "牧首的意思，當然和你差不多嘛——“別多管閒事”。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#2$2"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1780_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#8$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蕾繆安，我知道你是好心，不過你這是對我的不信任哦。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#8$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#8$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前輩，還請你理解。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#8$2"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#6$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "育嬰聖堂，這座不知從何時起就睥睨著拉特蘭城的巨型結構……", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#6$2"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不論是你、帕特里奇昂閣下還是那位牧首，都許諾未來將從此處誕生。就連那位製造爆炸的“嫌犯”，似乎也對它很有興趣。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#6$2"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你一定比我更理解，負責情報與國安的第七廳，怎麼能忽視這樣萬眾矚目的焦點呢？", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1780_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "理解理解。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#1$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1785_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "麻煩借過一下。", "name": "帶路的保育員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1785_1#1$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_churchfootstep", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_001", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.2}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_932_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.2}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_003", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.2}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1041_angel2_1#1$5", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.5, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.2}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1255_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.2}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "保育員帶著一隊人經過，腳步聲敲醒了空曠的啟聖大廳。"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隊伍中的人來自不同種族，沒有一個人說話，但所有人都好奇地觀察著這個陌生的空間。"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蕾繆安連忙側身讓路。"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#5$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#5$2"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1780_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼了，蕾繆安樞機？", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#4$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#2$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……沒什麼。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#2$2"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是想說，好奇心害死菲林，我要是繼續堅持，可能真的就被前輩投訴了。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}